statements.sql:
insert into `core_quiz_question_answers` (`paragraph`, `is_correct`, `core_quiz_questions_id`, `create_user`, `updated_at`, `created_at`) values ('

Because being in nature helps you reconnect with your true self. It makes you feel whole. It triggers the release of oxytocin, endorphin, and dopamine—chemicals that boost your well-being. At the same time, it lowers cortisol. That means less stress. That’s when you’ll feel more alive & content.

Plus, spending time outdoors also improves your focus, problem-solving skills, and creativity by as much as 50%. Those are powerful perks. So why not take a break? Spend a weekend in a nearby park or mountain, and let go of whatever’s weighing you down.

After all, nothing is more fulfilling than a feeling of absolute well-being, inner resilience, and productivity. Don’t believe us? You can see it for yourself.

', 0, 89, 6, '2025-06-29 18:51:19', '2025-06-29 18:51:19')
bindings:
Because being in nature helps you reconnect with your true self. It makes you feel whole. It triggers the release of oxytocin, endorphin, and dopamine—chemicals that boost your well-being. At the same time, it lowers cortisol. That means less stress. That’s when you’ll feel more alive & content.

Plus, spending time outdoors also improves your focus, problem-solving skills, and creativity by as much as 50%. Those are powerful perks. So why not take a break? Spend a weekend in a nearby park or mountain, and let go of whatever’s weighing you down.

After all, nothing is more fulfilling than a feeling of absolute well-being, inner resilience, and productivity. Don’t believe us? You can see it for yourself.
